    <div class="Question">
        <div class="quest quest1">
            <h3>What services do you offer?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            <p>We offer comprehensive wedding planning services including full wedding coordination, partial planning, day-of coordination, venue selection, vendor management, budget planning, design and decor, timeline creation, and rehearsal coordination. Our team handles every detail to ensure your special day is flawless.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quest quest2">
            <h3>How can I book your services?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            <p>Booking our services is easy. Simply contact us through our website contact form, email us at info@dreamday.com, or call us at +1 (555) 123-4567. We'll schedule a complimentary consultation to discuss your vision, needs, and budget. After our meeting, we'll provide a customized proposal and contract for your review.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quest quest3">
            <h3>How much does it cost?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            <p>Our wedding planning costs are tailored to each couple's needs. Pricing depends on the level of service (full planning starts at $3,500, partial planning from $2,000, and day-of coordination from $1,200), wedding complexity, guest count, and location. During your free consultation, we'll discuss creating your dream wedding within your budget.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quest quest4">
            <h3>Do you offer customizable packages?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            <p>Absolutely! We understand every couple is unique. Our packages are completely customizable - you can mix and match services to create your perfect plan. Popular add-ons include honeymoon planning, engagement party coordination, and post-wedding brunch organization. We'll work closely with you to design a package that fits your specific requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quest quest5">
            <h3>Can you assist with vendor selection?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            <p>Yes! We have an extensive network of trusted vendors we've worked with for years. We'll recommend photographers, florists, caterers, musicians, and other professionals that match your style and budget. Our vendor relationships often mean exclusive deals and priority booking for our clients. We also handle all vendor communications and contracts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quest quest6">
            <h3>How far in advance should we book your services?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            <p>We recommend booking as soon as you have your date and venue secured, typically 9-12 months before the wedding. For full planning services, 12-18 months is ideal. However, we've successfully planned beautiful weddings with shorter timelines. Contact us regardless of your timeline - we'll do our best to accommodate you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quest quest7">
            <h3>Do you handle weddings outside of our local area?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            <p>Yes, we specialize in destination weddings! We've planned celebrations across the country and internationally. For non-local weddings, we include additional planning trips in our package to ensure everything is perfect. Travel expenses are calculated separately based on your wedding location.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="quest quest8">
            <h3>What makes your wedding planners different?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
            <p>Our planners bring an average of 10+ years experience, personalized attention (you'll work directly with your lead planner), and a stress-free approach. We're known for our creative problem-solving, meticulous organization, and ability to bring unique visions to life. Most importantly, we treat every wedding as if it were our own.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
